Titolo: Golden Tee Golf

Anno: 1989

Descrizione: Golden Tee Golf is a golf arcade game series by Incredible Technologies. Its signature feature is the use of a trackball to determine the power, direction and curve of the player's golf shot. Play modes include casual 18-hole golf, closest to the pin, and online tournaments.
One of the longest running arcade game series, Golden Tee has maintained a large following and a competitive tournament scene.